<sect1 id="dir_65d165468c717c67bace063bdb86ff73_1autotoc_md272">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::match</title><para>Match state management system for the helios engine.</para>
<para>This module provides a rule-based state machine for managing match states (e.g., Warmup, PlayerSpawn, Playing) with transitions, listeners, and command-driven state changes.</para>
</sect1>
