<sect1 id="dir_65d165468c717c67bace063bdb86ff73_1autotoc_md274">
<title>Architecture</title><para>1. <bold>MatchStateManager</bold> holds the transition rules and processes state commands 2. <bold>MatchStateCommand</bold> encapsulates a transition request 3. <bold>MatchStateTransitionRule</bold> defines valid from -&gt; to transitions with optional guards 4. <bold>MatchStateTransitionListener</bold> implementations react to state changes</para>
</sect1>
